# DA-5: Avoid Overengineering
VERSION: 1.0.0
PRIORITY: SYSTEM
SCOPE: All pattern and abstraction proposals

## CATEGORY CONTEXT
- Overengineering: Introducing complexity beyond actual requirements.

ENFORCE: Every non-trivial pattern must have documented justification tied to a real requirement.
PROHIBIT: Patterns that add no measurable value; premature or overly generic abstractions.
ON VIOLATION: Escalate to Design Review Skill; suggest simplification.
